images.prompt: A hyperrealistic vision of an ethereal she-golem, her form shimmering with intricate metal petals that ripple and fold like a blooming mechanism, illuminated by floating prism light casting shifting hues of digital mint and shadow bronze across her textured metallic surface, as glitch-wrapped perspectives distort her divine assemblage into a surreal, multidimensional tableau that blends organic grace with mechanized elegance, evoking a sense of mystic power imbued with surreal digital artistry and immersive depth.
